## Installation

Install all the dependencies
```
npm install
```

Download SQL and create .env with the following variable
```
DB_ROOT_PASSWORD=INSERT_MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD_HERE
```

Generate prisma client
```
npm run prisma
```

## To create a new instance:

Create new entry in `ecosystem.config`, and define a name for the env file by setting ENV_FILE variable.
Now create a `.env.ENV_FILE` with the BOT_TOKEN and DATABASE_URL variables

## Production Script

```
npm run build
npm run start
```

## Development Script

```
ENV_FILE=APP_NAME npm run dev
```